Contains the vislib visualizations. These are the classical area/line/bar, gauge/goal and heatmap charts. We want to replace them with elastic-charts.

Contact [@elastic/kibana-visualizations](https://github.com/orgs/elastic/teams/kibana-visualizations) for questions regarding this plugin.
